OL,6,FFormer prime ministers Boris Johnson
OL,7,Fand Liz Truss both received #18,660
OL,8,Fafter resigning, while Kwasi Kwarteng
OL,9,Fwas given #16,876 when he was forced
OL,10,Fout as chancellor after less than six
OL,11,Fweeks in the job, according to
OL,12,FGovernment figures.
